The '''Isticians''' were the native race of the irradiated [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Istic II]]. Due to radiation bombardment, the Isticians mutated into a variety of forms, sizes, and colors. When Istic II was colonized by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], the Empire declared the Isticians subsentient; this allowed the local Imperial governor to encourage the hunting of Isticians to make room for [[Human/Legends|Human]] settlers.

